<footer>The device, called the Autographer, can be worn around the neck, clipped to clothing or placed in a particular vantage point and uses five in-built sensors and software developed by Microsoft Corp to chose the best moment to capture an image without any intervention from the user.<br>(Autographer.com)</footer>
